actions.title: Deployment proxy
actions.description: A deployer proxy for deploying all Poof contracts via CREATE2

actions.title: POOF Token
actions.description: The Poof.cash governance token. At deployment, POOF will be distributed to several timelock, mining, and airdrop contracts.

actions.title: Release POOF Token
actions.description: A non-transferrable Poof.cash governance token. ReleasePOOF can be converted into POOF on a linear release schedule. Release starts at timestamp 1625130000 and ends at timestamp 1719478800.

actions.title: Governance Timelock
actions.description: The timelock contract for Poof's on-chain governance. This timelock is owned by the Governance proxy contract and will be allocated the POOF tokens inteded for Poof's governance. This timelock will also have rights to any governance-only functions of the Poof protocol.

actions.title: Reserve Timelock
actions.description: The timelock contract for the Celo reserve. This timelock will be allocated the POOF tokens intended for the Celo reserve.

actions.title: Liquidity Timelock
actions.description: The timelock contract for managing the Ubeswap POOF liquidity. This contract will be allocated the POOF tokens intended for seeding POOF liquidity.

actions.title: Romulus Implementation
actions.description: The logic contract for Poof's on-chain governance.

actions.title: Romulus Proxy
actions.description: The proxy contract for Poof's on-chain governance. This enables Poof's governance to be upgradeable.

actions.title: Governance Allocator
actions.description: This contract allocates POOF to the governance timelock at a linear rate. Allocation begins at timestamp 1625130000 and ends at timestamp 1722268800.

actions.title: Celo Reserve Allocator
actions.description: This contract allocates POOF to the Celo reserve timelock at a linear rate. Allocation begins at timestamp 1625130000 and ends at timestamp 1722268800.

actions.title: Reward Verifier
actions.description: ZkSnark verifier smart contract for mining rewards

actions.title: Withdraw Verifier
actions.description: ZkSnark verifier smart contract for reward withdrawals

actions.title: Tree Update Verifier
actions.description: ZkSnark verifier smart contract for validation for account merkle tree updates

actions.title: Reward Swap
actions.description: AMM that allows users to swap Anonymity Points for POOF

actions.title: Poseidon hasher 2
actions.description: Poseidon hash function for 2 arguments

actions.title: Poseidon hasher 3
actions.description: Poseidon hash function for 3 arguments

actions.title: Poof Proxy
actions.description: This contract registers Poof deposits and withdrawals for the mining contract and proxies the privacy contracts.

actions.title: Poof Trees
actions.description: Merkle tree with information about Poof deposits and withdrawals

actions.title: Miner
actions.description: This contract enables users to mine Anonymity Points (AP) and swap AP for POOF.

actions.title: vPOOF Token
actions.description: A non-transferrable voucher (vPOOF) that can be swapped at a 1:1 rate for POOF. The voucher expires 15724800 seconds after contract deployment. vPOOF will be airdropped to addressed that used Poof, locked CELO, or deposited into Tornado.cash

actions.title: vPOOF Airdrop #1
actions.description: This contract airdrops vPOOF to at most 180 addresses
